(Lunarpine in wolf mode right?)

::Shadow Wing::

She walked down the hall and came to the room where the others were 
gathered.  She saw Lunarpine there and smiled to herself.  She walked 
up to him and patted him on the head. She looked down a him and 
smiled. "So what's going on? How are the plans coming?"
